<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="9" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Shell relatively medium-sized, moderately solid, sculptured with granulation, a faint pattern of spiral bands on the last whorl, the interstices about as wide as the bands, last whorl inflated, suture deeply descending in front, peristome hardly expanded and reflexed.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="9" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Dimensions.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Shell height 48.3, diameter 22.7 mm.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
